Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狮堂光、龙咲海、凤凰寺风三人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.78,0:01:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被美艾诺公主召唤成为
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.15,0:01:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救异世界锡菲罗的魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而三人打倒最后的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.49,0:01:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图的时候终于来临
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.96,0:02:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图挡在三人面前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.69,0:02:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的攻击非常惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光等人多次被轰飞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.63,0:02:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 光等三人同心合力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.04,0:02:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使出合体魔法“闪光之螺旋”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于消灭了谢加图
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说中的魔法骑士!\N惊人的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.25,0:03:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样 我们终于能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主的心愿了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唤醒魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒捉走公主的谢加图
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样 这个锡菲罗就得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能回去东京了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…小海、小风
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和小海小风你们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被召唤来锡菲罗这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真幸运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果只是我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定不能这么努力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一样啊 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果只是我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我或许会惊徨失措
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在最初的森林就被魔物吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果只是我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:54.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在异世界怎样行动才好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 小海 小风
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主一定在这座城堡内
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样进去?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是水晶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是保护这座城堡的结界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那声音是…雷亚斯!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 谢加图己经…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座城堡是艾美诺公主的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑟列斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个结界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是由艾美诺公主的心筑成的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温达姆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的魔法能击毁结界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这结界内的城堡里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗的柱在这座城堡里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:04:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,异世界的少女们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士的真正敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强大得是以往的敌人根本无法比拟的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗已经完结了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去艾美诺公主那里吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水之龙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碧岚疾风
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是个女人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在艾蒂露娜之泉\N救了我们时…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:07:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外表是个年幼的小女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是艾美诺公主吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确很像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在艾蒂露娜之泉\N见过的女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮的金发
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有眼睛的颜色也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是被你\N召唤来的异世界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们遵照导师古列夫的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到创师普蕾西雅铸造武器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.42,0:07:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由莫歌拿带领
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功唤醒魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普蕾西雅豁出性命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为我们铸造了武器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫遵守和你的承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,协助我们成为魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然他被谢加图变成石头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.71,0:07:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图已经被打倒\N他一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.38,0:07:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 艾美诺公主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点不对劲儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死谢加图的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死我心爱的谢加图的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罪无可恕!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔神的体内!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔神救了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城堡崩塌了 快出去外面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个不是艾美诺公主吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人是锡菲罗的柱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是被艾美诺公主\N唤来的吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.43,0:09:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召唤异世界的人的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有锡菲罗的柱才能使用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们为何会被\N艾美诺公主攻击?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是魔法骑士真正要对付的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么一回事!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图的剑…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:10:01.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死谢加图的魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罪无可恕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用谢加图\N的这把剑杀死你们!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不可饶恕!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉…厉害!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一击就令城堡粉碎!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的是艾美诺公主吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是锡菲罗的…艾美诺!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召唤我们来锡菲罗的是你吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你为何攻击我们!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的究竟是…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护之风
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.61,0:11:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这声音是…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在艾蒂露娜之泉听过的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是当时的艾美诺公主的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那部魔神里的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:45.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不是艾美诺公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的艾美诺公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.63,0:11:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍然被软禁在其他地方!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主 你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这个人就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这部魔神里的就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.28,0:12:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是舍弃了\N锡菲罗之柱的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢地选择了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只为所爱的人而活的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所爱的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你把我们从东京
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唤来这个锡菲罗的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.17,0:12:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在东京塔时的确听到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“救救这个世界”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“传说中的…魔法骑士们”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我召唤传说中的魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了拯救这个锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要打倒谢加图
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个锡菲罗不是就有救了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是因为谢加图软禁了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你不能再为锡菲罗祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:12:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以锡菲罗就变成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:13:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充斥着魔物的不安定世界吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是谢加图…他的错!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.87,0:13:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是…我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗是个\N一切取决于心的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而柱就以意志的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支撑着这个世界的法规和秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柱只需要一直
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为这个世界的安定和幸福祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对谢加图…\N那个身为神官的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱上了他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱上了谢加图的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得关心谢加图多于锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘记了身为\N锡菲罗的柱的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图…\N只要他得到幸福就行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然想着那种可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…\N谢加图为何要捉走你?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.18,0:14:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也发觉了我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算一直隐瞒下去的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样 谢加图也爱上了我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是\N我们的心愿绝对不能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是锡菲罗的柱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能成为任何一个人的所有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我始终无法死心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能忘记他…\N忘记谢加图!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.78,0:15:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么\N这个世界充斥着魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,责任并不在于\N谢加图…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗是意志的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有心祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从哪里也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.46,0:15:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有任何障碍也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都能为世界的安定祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你为何召唤我们!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我召唤魔法骑士是为了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要你们把我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀…死…!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柱不容许自己选择死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而锡菲罗的人也不能加害于柱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柱有其他人\N不能使用的召唤魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是从锡菲罗以外的异世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唤来骑士\N把自己置诸死地的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:16:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图想阻止我们\N成为魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.95,0:16:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了不让我们杀死你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧口中的传说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是指这回事吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗有危机时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士会从异世界来临
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唤醒三部魔神 成为魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把失去\N谢加图的悲伤化为仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,创造了这种魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士驾御魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为以血肉之躯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本赢不了锡菲罗的柱!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士的真正敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强大得是以往的敌人根本无法比拟的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是指这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢杀死谢加图!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀死你们!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用谢加图这把剑!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.63,0:16:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我求你们!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:17:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经快要消失了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.17,0:17:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仇恨和杀意…\N即将充斥我的心!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候 我一定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈求锡菲罗完全崩溃和毁灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.59,0:17:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说中的魔法骑士们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.36,0:17:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 拯救锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎可以…!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!  小光!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.71,0:17:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.22,0:17:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你早就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主的心意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么方法能救她吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主不用死的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果现在的柱不死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的柱就不会诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗除了等待新的柱诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别无他途
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是爱上一个人 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她为何一定要死!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是锡菲罗的法规
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎能这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.17,0:18:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.84,0:18:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你们实现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主真正的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.91,0:18:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的…愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我求你们 魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实现我真正的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.52,0:19:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我到谢加图身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.59,0:19:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我…今后…\N能只是想着谢加图
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能永远和他一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实现我第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是最后一个的任性愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于可以…\N只是属于你的了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.79,0:20:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:21:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常刺眼的强光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.31,0:21:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么呢?小光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…做梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.57,0:21:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想再去锡菲罗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.27,0:21:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次要为了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.61,0:21:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为柱的艾美诺公主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍而重之守护的锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.95,0:21:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽自己的一分力…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:10.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着停不了的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:21.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱紧不能转让的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.16,0:00:29.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士雷亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:37.20,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,海的颜色逐渐染成红色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:39.17,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,无重力状态
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.21,0:00:44.01,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,想就此被风带走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然以不认输的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:53.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,跳过经常跳不过的栏杆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:01:02.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,但用不完的实力是谁所赐?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:09.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着停不了的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:15.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱紧不能转让的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:20.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,心底不褪色的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:25.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,背着阳光透出耀眼光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:22.59,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,面带最美的笑容用力踏脚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.29,0:22:31.09,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,逆风也不可以沮丧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:38.09,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不输给悲伤的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.43,0:22:48.80,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,悄悄地告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.13,0:22:55.13,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着广阔海洋前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.04,0:23:04.77,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 你的瞳孔终有一日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.31,0:23:12.82,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,会在阳光下散发光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.15,0:23:22.96,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不要灰心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.09,0:23:31.95,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,把信念化成奔向明日的勇气
